{"type":"text","timestamp":1778673553186,"sessionID":"ses_1decbe565ffeNuoIzkEVPLZogL","part":{"id":"prt_e21348656001KsNwhoDA3A5f43","messageID":"msg_e21344845001Vt3gw6C3G8qDyK","sessionID":"ses_1decbe565ffeNuoIzkEVPLZogL","type":"text","text":"The prior micro-opt wins were narrow Fmax/routing reductions; most CPI-oriented shortcuts and wider control rewrites regressed. I’m choosing a conservative single-file forwarding-cone cleanup rather than another predictor, load-bypass, or control-bundle split.","time":{"start":1778673550934,"end":1778673553184},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_06a75f301f62641f016a04678eccb08199978a0c6e6f9d6a2b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
