t fixed byte/halfword mask decoding while preserving misalignment gating.\"\n","additions":24,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-001-r12s0.yaml","time":{"start":1778673595718,"end":1778673595722}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_080256804c809d8e016a0467abf2ac819ab6d64d3f849d2c29"}},"id":"prt_e2134f811001OB1x3dXAFbOlGQ","sessionID":"ses_1decbe565ffeNuoIzkEVPLZogL","messageID":"msg_e2134ad12001Y675ZjjTH00lJG"}}
