{"type":"text","timestamp":1778657244686,"sessionID":"ses_1dfc49f0fffecJpc9qvxOyv2Yx","part":{"id":"prt_e203bb45d001HOsduRx1ZAH3qj","messageID":"msg_e203b84f6001C7ABRQVa76v0sX","sessionID":"ses_1dfc49f0fffecJpc9qvxOyv2Yx","type":"text","text":"There are no recorded lessons and the only prior `micro_opt` entry is the baseline retest, so I’m proposing a focused CPI/Fmax micro-optimization rather than avoiding a known failed path.","time":{"start":1778657244253,"end":1778657244683},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_081c22f388089327016a0427dc03308198a403c109ed192dfd","phase":"commentary"}}}}
