{"type":"text","timestamp":1778666685790,"sessionID":"ses_1df34bda8ffeBBsqjqFjT3Mfmt","part":{"id":"prt_e20cbc489001iNpBuWHepaHnxe","messageID":"msg_e20cb8a6f001ylqksoMEmtINqi","sessionID":"ses_1df34bda8ffeBBsqjqFjT3Mfmt","type":"text","text":"The prior successful micro-opts were Fmax-focused pruning; the failed ones either changed operand reporting or added repacking/fanout. I’m going to write a narrower Fmax hypothesis around reducing reset/data muxing on wide pipeline bundles while keeping valid/trap/control reset behavior explicit.","time":{"start":1778666685577,"end":1778666685789},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_07f0266fa81655e6016a044cbd77308198818e6941ddd1db76","phase":"commentary"}}}}
