{"type":"text","timestamp":1778661444468,"sessionID":"ses_1df852e9effeLUwZ055H2LGRh6","part":{"id":"prt_e207bc8710010rBXbmDeODl2Hl","messageID":"msg_e207b308b001jbvwbuRc9AA1iN","sessionID":"ses_1df852e9effeLUwZ055H2LGRh6","type":"text","text":"The relevant history rules out another early-branch/prediction attempt for this slot. I’m writing a structural front-end buffering hypothesis that targets the random iStall/back-end stall interaction without changing RVFI retirement or the branch resolution contract.","time":{"start":1778661443697,"end":1778661444467},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d7f6be6d43598e6016a0438439724819a945b4278b120a840","phase":"commentary"}}}}
