{"type":"text","timestamp":1778666672958,"sessionID":"ses_1df34bcc7ffeyhdId4u5zcI80E","part":{"id":"prt_e20cb92b2001s69biIya47G1UG","messageID":"msg_e20cb6c39001ckZuzX2RFhQDeB","sessionID":"ses_1df34bcc7ffeyhdId4u5zcI80E","type":"text","text":"Prior structural wins were back-end decoupling and MDU isolation; front-end retiming/skid/prediction attempts either broke or regressed. I’m going to propose a narrow back-end structural follow-up: deepen the posted store buffer to absorb short store bursts without touching fetch or redirect timing.","time":{"start":1778666672818,"end":1778666672957},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_010d73fe47a1b80d016a044cb0b790819a8d47f3537677e243","phase":"commentary"}}}}
