{"type":"text","timestamp":1778671865329,"sessionID":"ses_1dee5ad85ffeMCgdyu2m0J6hqP","part":{"id":"prt_e211ac3a0001njQXamBZ4gkdCZ","messageID":"msg_e211a8253001UT8JoBKpmrvXz6","sessionID":"ses_1dee5ad85ffeMCgdyu2m0J6hqP","type":"text","text":"Predictor history is consistently negative when it adds IF/ID redirect sources or prediction metadata. I’m going to write a deliberately conservative predictor hypothesis: a tiny EX-updated loop-exit confidence bit used only to suppress learning/prediction on branches that recently exited, keeping the predictor single-entry and avoiding wider tables or immediate decode.","time":{"start":1778671862688,"end":1778671865327},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_01894f43d6a6ec96016a0460f693dc81998b450fa087d7a090","phase":"commentary"}}}}
