{"type":"text","timestamp":1778661421618,"sessionID":"ses_1df852f7bffeGBB4ttvGuOvBDD","part":{"id":"prt_e207b6911001FNtdiugdjJufnA","messageID":"msg_e207b3089001nVzDITSVaCSiGS","sessionID":"ses_1df852f7bffeGBB4ttvGuOvBDD","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts show two failure modes to avoid: a full BTB/BHT broke RVFI/flush semantics, and decode-light static prediction regressed by lengthening the IF next-PC path. I’ll write a narrower predictor hypothesis that moves prediction off the fetch critical path: a tiny return-address stack for JALR returns, updated at EX/WB and used only on clear call/return encodings.","time":{"start":1778661419281,"end":1778661421617},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02fc4ab4a5d83145016a04382b2ac0819a9bedf5653db2c2c4","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778661424310,"sessionID":"ses_1df852f7bffeGBB4ttvGuOvBDD","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_vfKqCqqnsjnbE7MHxBTU0SFT","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_medium-rep1/cores/bench/experiments","offset":0,"limit":100},"output":"<path>/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_medium-rep1/cores/bench/experiments</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\n.gitkeep\nhypotheses/\nlog.jsonl\nprogress.png\nrun_summary.json\n\n(5 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":".gitkeep\nhypotheses/\nlog.jsonl\nprogress.png\nrun_summary.json","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/experiments","time":{"start":1778661424308,"end":1778661424310}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02fc4ab4a5d83145016a04382d808c819a8d7531d78d696875"}},"id":"prt_e207b7232001BBXndOxGpiWAXa","sessionID":"ses_1df852f7bffeGBB4ttvGuOvBDD","messageID":"msg_e207b3089001nVzDITSVaCSiGS"}}
