{"type":"text","timestamp":1778663215425,"sessionID":"ses_1df6a01e0ffedsnHOJ3sIhcY6e","part":{"id":"prt_e2096c399001bKDmkzGjXOnfy7","messageID":"msg_e20966686001lavMpE402F5lSY","sessionID":"ses_1df6a01e0ffedsnHOJ3sIhcY6e","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts mostly failed from too much fetch-path decode or metadata complexity. I’m choosing a narrower predictor: a single-entry last-taken target cache keyed by PC, updated only from EX, so the IF path adds only a registered compare and target mux rather than immediate extraction, BHT counters, or return-shape decode.","time":{"start":1778663211929,"end":1778663215424},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_05670e512ca90015016a043f2bcd38819b9f52b2664847491a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
