o undef.\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] base: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_medium-rep1/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-4723/../../cores/bench-4723/wrapper.sv:39: ERROR: Cell instance refers to port io_rvfi_valid_1 which does not exist in module core!.\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] base: finished (returncode=1)\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] base: task failed. ERROR.\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] summary: Elapsed clock time [H:MM:SS (secs)]: 0:00:00 (0)\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] summary: Elapsed process time [H:MM:SS (secs)]: 0:00:00 (0)\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] summary: engine_0 (smtbmc bitwuzla) did not return a status\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] summary: engine_0 did not produce any traces\nSBY  9:49:42 [causal_ch0] DONE (ERROR, rc=16)\n\nFull run log: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_medium-rep1/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260513-002-r15s1/formal/last_run-4723.log\nPer-check logs in: /Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_medium-rep1/cores/bench/worktrees/hyp-20260513-002-r15s1/formal/riscv-formal/cores/bench-4723/checks/<check>/logfile.txt\n","exit":1,"description":"Run bench single-issue formal checks","truncated":true,"outputPath":"/Users/bonetto/.local/share/opencode/tool-output/tool_e2162cd92001B6JQgrOZiupnuC"},"title":"Run bench single-issue formal checks","time":{"start":1778676584082,"end":1778676584096}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0499bc7d7d0a1934016a0473620a6881999a4a86a498df62b3"}},"id":"prt_e2162b75d0010uJgXx2AdfdWBy","sessionID":"ses_1de9ecc0cffe0G79S3mVPj20U0","messageID":"msg_e2162a66d001wwLY4XXzS6zC39"}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1778676584183,"sessionID":"ses_1de9ecc0cffe0G79S3mVPj20U0","part":{"id":"prt_e2162cef5001pZYCLnfZ7SQUAZ","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"9d92a75d914f84af871bfdb900a54fd24bb2971c","messageID":"msg_e2162a66d001wwLY4XXzS6zC39","sessionID":"ses_1de9ecc0cffe0G79S3mVPj20U0","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":48800,"input":505,"output":149,"reasoning":18,"cache":{"write":0,"read":48128}},"cost":0}}
